{"tid":2028741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[拉攏藍絲.港豬］國安法搞到無Netflix 睇.無switch 玩.無IG上","createTime":"2020-05-22T03:15:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T03:24:46.000Z","uid":18577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6a79f9e08fd8aad43a485e049720a6fc64b7e3b0","tid":2028741,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:15:34.000Z","msg":"恭喜個班沉默咗一年..依一年入面繼續飲飲食食..吃喝玩樂嘅人<br />\n<br />\n好快大家連switch 都無得玩..唔好再講咩動森..mario..係鬼國入面連部switch都比人維穩..乜都無得你玩<br />\n<br />\n你想睇個電視咩..sorry!!鬼國係無Netflix 嘅..要睇就睇央視啦你<br />\n<br />\n好啦..game又無得玩..電視又無得睇..諗住玩下電話..連IG..fb都無得玩..<br />\n<br />\n都唔好講班廢老終於都識玩十幾年前嘅產物fb..你重想好似以前咁留言鬧港獨鬧黃絲咩..諗多咗啦！fb都無得你玩啦<br />\n<br />\n如果你身邊重有堆藍絲..記得記得提佢哋立即剷咗個Fb..wtsapp..你點知國安法一過有以上ac嘅會唔會比人當你叛國罪架<br />\n<br />\n等佢哋知道自由嘅可貴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">真係好無助</span>"},{"pid":"4118f68b9ded91ab37f642a9bb50335f068d6e8d","tid":2028741,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b65b1ae54a13c7a334fbea5cab33d75aa68fc6","tid":2028741,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e525d5963e3ed830a0056c2b7906863adc8c56d2","tid":2028741,"uid":85396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:21:45.000Z","msg":"我本來中立, 宜家轉黃了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" cl